Here are the interested parties:


Book
    interested in: patches

Book control panel
    interested in: Book state changes


Library
    interested in: All book state changes
    interested in: Library events (add/remove)


bookNotificationStream - pipes patch events and Book state events for specific book

LibraryNotificationStream - pipes all Book state events + Library events



bookNotificationStream add listener to Library.Book[url][id].on('change')

LibraryNotificationStream.add listener to Library.Book[url][id].on('change')

Patch Event - Book[url][id].emit('patch')

